data.description: ** ASSUMABLE LOAN AVAILABLE ** Welcome to your dream home! This lovely property is nestled on a spacious greenbelt lot, offering you the tranquility and privacy you've been searching for. With solar panels providing efficient energy solutions, you'll enjoy low utility bills while contributing to a sustainable future. Inside, you'll be greeted by the timeless elegance of tile flooring throughout the downstairs area, creating a sleek and easy-to-maintain living space.    The heart of this home is the inviting island kitchen, perfect for culinary enthusiasts and entertaining guests. Adjacent to the laundry room, you'll find a convenient utility desk-a quiet oasis for studying or working from home. This home is thoughtfully updated with modern light fixtures and fresh interior paint, enhancing its overall appeal.    Step outside to the covered patio, overlooking the flat backyard, with no rear neighbors, perfect for outdoor gatherings and relaxation. With great curb appeal highlighted by the covered front porch, this home is the epitome of comfort, style, and convenience. Located in a prime spot, you'll have easy access to Loop 410, Hwy 90, parks, golf courses, and Air Force bases. Don't miss your chance to make it yours!
